    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164050/extras/bbdc3abc7d5c4ad1155b4c629376f349.poster.avif?t=1741008820\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164050/extras/bbdc3abc7d5c4ad1155b4c629376f349.webm?t=1741008820\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164050/extras/bbdc3abc7d5c4ad1155b4c629376f349.mp4?t=1741008820\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>360°2D Shooter</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is an STG where you fly 360° around the stage and engage in dogfights.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It requires a good feeling of flying a fighter plane and shooting accuracy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Always Bullet Time</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have the superpower to stop time every frame.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your bullets will always hit and your enemies' bullets will always be avoided.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It should be the easiest shooter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But it is like getting into a car and resisting the urge to step on the gas pedal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164050/extras/4ca2c16b2c00a2ceafb19d7d709cbfc0.poster.avif?t=1741008820\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164050/extras/4ca2c16b2c00a2ceafb19d7d709cbfc0.webm?t=1741008820\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164050/extras/4ca2c16b2c00a2ceafb19d7d709cbfc0.mp4?t=1741008820\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Machine Customization</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can tune your fighter between stages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Is it the turning performance, the boost gauge, the ammunition load, or the reload time for each weapon?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Both the operating technique and machine maintenance in racing games are important, and maintenance is not simply a factor that makes you stronger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The same is true in this game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DemoVersion</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Episode1 is distributed free of charge until Ending.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is to fully convey the special experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you like it, please subscribe to our WishList.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We are planning to produce up to Episode3.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(English translation of Episode3 may be delayed)</p>",
